					<description><![CDATA[<p>Find out everything you've ever wanted to know about event tracking in Google Analytics 4. Including how it works, why it's important, and how to set up custom events using Google Tag Manager.</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/07/07/google-analytics-4-event-tracking">Demystifying Event Tracking in Google Analytics 4: A Comprehensive Tutorial for Marketers</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
