<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2021/11/15/multi-touch-attribution">Multi-Touch Attribution: Tips &#038; Types, Which Model is Right?</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
